7.0  EXAMPLES

The following sequence of commands  to  MAKVFU  will  produce  a  file
equivalent to the standard VFU file NORMAL.VFU which is distributed by
DEC.  It is possible that other sequences of input  will  produce  the
same VFU file.

     LENGTH 66
     PAGE-SIZE 60
     CHANNEL 1 EVERY 60
     CHANNEL 2 EVERY 30
     CHANNEL 3 EVERY 2
     CHANNEL 4 EVERY 3
     CHANNEL 5 ALL
     FORMS-BREAK 5
     CHANNEL 6 EVERY 10
     CHANNEL 7 EVERY 20
     CHANNEL 8 ALL
     CHANNEL 12 BOTTOM



